                    "line_text": "Calmes comme un bétail stupide.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme hier et comme demain,\nD'un pas tantôt lent ou rapide\nElles arpentent le chemin,\nCalmes comme un bétail stupide."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Leurs corsages voluptueux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Provoquent des épithalames.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Alors des mortels vertueux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
